OL,3,CMurder investigation launched
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Portadown
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched following the death of a man
OL,8,Fin Portadown.
OL,10,FThe man aged in his 40s was found
OL,11,Finjured following an altercation at a
OL,12,Fproperty in the Ranfurley Road area
OL,13,Faround 11pm on Thursday.
OL,15,FEmergency services attended but the
OL,16,Fman was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,18,FTwo men aged in their 50s have been
OL,19,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,20,Fare in police custody.
